# ============================================================
# NAME:    NinjaTrader / Tradovate
# TYPE:    Program (desktop + web trading platform)
# REPO:    https://github.com/kevshen13/surge-rules
# UPDATED: 2026-07-08
# DATA:    NinjaTrader routes market data / orders via Continuum (CQG) or Rithmic
#          -> CQG rules live in cqg.list, Rithmic rules in rithmic.list. Keep them on the SAME exit as NinjaTrader.
# NOTE:    LAN trading PCs proxy through Surge, so PROCESS-NAME does NOT apply to them;
#          the DOMAIN / IP rules below do the routing.
# SOURCE:  Tradovate/NinjaTrader Partner API docs (production, staging, client, market-data, replay endpoints).
# ============================================================

# ---- Local-process hints (only effective if NinjaTrader runs on the Surge host itself) ----
PROCESS-NAME,NinjaTrader
PROCESS-NAME,NinjaTrader 8
PROCESS-NAME,Tradovate

# ---- NinjaTrader / Tradovate domains ----
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ninjatrader.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ninjatrader.dev
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tradovate.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tradovateapi.com
DOMAIN,trader.tradovate.com
DOMAIN,web.ninjatrader.com
DOMAIN,dashboards.tradovate.com
DOMAIN,api.tradovate.com
DOMAIN,auth.tradovate.com
DOMAIN,community.tradovate.com
DOMAIN,live.tradovateapi.com
DOMAIN,demo.tradovateapi.com
DOMAIN,login.tradovate.com
DOMAIN,md.tradovateapi.com
DOMAIN,replay.tradovateapi.com
DOMAIN,web.tradovate.com

# ---- Partner API staging / development ----
DOMAIN,live-api.staging.ninjatrader.dev
DOMAIN,demo-api.staging.ninjatrader.dev
DOMAIN,md-api.staging.ninjatrader.dev
DOMAIN,replay.staging.ninjatrader.dev
DOMAIN,trader.staging.ninjatrader.dev
DOMAIN,web.staging.ninjatrader.dev
DOMAIN,dashboards.staging.ninjatrader.dev

